hibernate

Interface HibernateConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HibernateBgClient, HibernateBgClientWithHQL

    public interface HibernateConstants
    This interface defines all the constants for the default values of all the properties required by Hibernate client implementation.
    Author:
    Ankit Mutha (mutha.ankit@gmail.com)
